  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Coronavirus Job Retention Scheme: awareness, understanding and customer experience surveys
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Quantitative research with employers and employees to examine understanding, awareness and customer experience of the Coronavirus Job Retention Scheme.</p>

  </div>
</div>

